1932;;The Woman in Room 13;;American;;Henry King;;Elissa Landi, Ralph Bellamy;;mystery;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Woman_in_Room_13_(1932_film);;Laura Bruce is divorced from her husband following an unpleasant matrimonial term. She then marries Paul Ramsey, whom she has always loved. Dick Turner, his employer and enamored of Laura, sends her husband away on a business trip. A murder is committed and detective John Bruce seeks to fasten the crime upon Paul. After he fails to do so, a happy ending results.